      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RITZA ROCKER (1) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 6th at this track following on from a third place finish (23.28) there the start prior. Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Can bounce back. SAVINA (5) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (23.60) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Great chance to atone. LEKTRA BERT (2) turned in a plain run last time when seventh at Gunnedah over 431m behind Cowboy Carter (25.76) in a Grade 5. One of the better hopes. MAJOR FLIRT (7) generally performs well here at this distance.",
